	<Title>北京东城当代MOMA幼儿园多名孩子呕吐 被疑食物中毒</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime"> 2014-03-27 08:46:44</ReportTime>|来源：大公财经

<Content>　　
<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Participant sid="s">大公财经</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">3月27日</Time>北京<Denoter did="d1" type="statement">报道</Denoter></Event>（记者 梁爽）
<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e2"><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">3月25日晚</Time>，<Participant sid="s2">北京市民李芳馨女士</Participant>(下称李女士，注：文中的李芳馨及其孩子洋洋皆为化名)向<Participant oid="o2">大公财经</Participant><Denoter did="d2" type="statement">反映</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e3"><Time tid="t3" type="relTime">本月20日</Time>，<Participant sid="s3">李女士的孩子洋洋</Participant>，放学<Denoter did="d3" type="action">回家</Denoter></Event>后
<Event eid="e4"><Denoter did="d4" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>头痛、发烧、上吐下泻的<Object oid="o4">症状</Object></Event>，“
<Event eid="e5">很可能是<Denoter did="d5" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter></Event>。”
</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e6"><Participant sid="s6">李女士</Participant><Denoter did="d6" type="statement">表示</Denoter></Event>，“
<Event eid="e7"><Participant sid="s7">园里的很多孩子</Participant>都<Denoter did="d7" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>了<Object oid="o7">类似情况</Object></Event>，大概有20多人”。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph>　　
<Sentence>对于这一事件，
<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e8"><Participant sid="s8">幼儿园负责人陈某</Participant><Denoter did="d8" type="statement">解释称</Denoter></Event>，“
<Event eid="e9"><Participant sid="s9">我们</Participant>已经把<Object oid="o9">孩子们吃的食物</Object><Denoter did="d9" type="movement">送去</Denoter><Location lid="l9" type="destination">东城区疾控防疫中心</Location></Event>
				<Event eid="e10">进行<Denoter did="d10" type="operation">化验</Denoter></Event>”，
<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e11"><Participant sid="s11">该负责人</Participant>在<Time tid="t11" type="relTime">接受大公财经记者采访时</Time><Denoter did="d11" type="statement">表示</Denoter></Event>，“
并不一定是食物中毒，也存在其他可能，要等<Event eid="e12"><Object sid="s12">检验报告</Object><Denoter did="d12" type="stateChange">出来</Denoter></Event>才能确定。”</Sentence></Paragraph>
<Paragraph>　　
<Sentence>
<Event eid="e13" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s13">李女士</Participant><Denoter did="d13" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>，“这种疾病可以传染，很多
<Event eid="e14"><Participant sid="s14">患儿家长</Participant>也<Denoter did="d14" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>了<Object oid="o14">同样症状</Object></Event>” 。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph>　　<Sentence>
				
<Event eid="e15" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s15">北京东城区疾控中心相关负责人</Participant><Denoter did="d15" type="statement">表示</Denoter></Event>，“
<Event eid="e16"><Participant sid="s16">我们</Participant>已经<Denoter did="d16" type="action">知道</Denoter></Event>
<Event eid="e17"><Participant sid="s17">当代MOMA幼儿园</Participant>疑似群体<Denoter did="d17" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter>事件</Event>，
<Event eid="e18"><Time tid="t18" type="relTime">现在</Time><Denoter did="d18" type="action">收到</Denoter><Object oid="o18">检测样本</Object></Event>
，<Event eid="e19" polarity="negative"><Object sid="s19">检测报告</Object>还没<Denoter did="d19" type="stateChange">出来</Denoter></Event>
”，此外，
<Event eid="e20" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s20">该负责人</Participant>还<Denoter did="d20" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>“这件事归北京东城区食药监局管，不方便透露更多消息”。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph>　　<Sentence>
<Event eid="e21"><Participant sid="s21">大公财经</Participant>将进一步<Denoter did="d21" type="action">关注</Denoter><Object oid="o21">此事</Object></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
